@TravelEase_HostAddress = http://localhost:5261

### ============================================================================
### BOOKING MANAGEMENT MODULE - COMPREHENSIVE ENDPOINTS
### ============================================================================

### 1. CREATE BOOKING (POST /api/bookings)
### Initiates a new booking/checkout with optional reservations
POST {{TravelEase_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerID": 101,
  "partnerID": 5,
  "itemType": "Flight",
  "date": "2026-05-25T14:00:00Z",
  "status": "Pending",
  "amount": 299.99,
  "reservations": [
    {
      "details": "Window seat 12A",
      "startDate": "2026-07-01T10:00:00Z",
      "endDate": "2026-07-01T18:00:00Z",
      "status": "Active"
    },
    {
      "details": "Hotel room 305",
      "startDate": "2026-07-01T20:00:00Z",
      "endDate": "2026-07-05T12:00:00Z",
      "status": "Active"
    }
  ]
}

###

### 2. GET ALL BOOKINGS (GET /api/bookings)
### Retrieves complete list of all bookings
GET {{TravelEase_HostAddress}}/api/bookings
Accept: application/json

###

### 3. GET BOOKING BY ID (GET /api/bookings/{bookingId})
### Retrieves a specific booking with all associated reservations
GET {{TravelEase_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/1
Accept: application/json

###

### 4. GET BOOKING HISTORY BY CUSTOMER (GET /api/bookings/customer/{customerId})
### Searches all bookings for a specific customer (booking history retrieval)
GET {{TravelEase_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/customer/101
Accept: application/json

###

### 5. SEARCH BOOKINGS BY STATUS (GET /api/bookings/status/{status})
### Filters bookings by status (Pending, Confirmed, Cancelled, etc.)
GET {{TravelEase_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/status/Pending
Accept: application/json

###

### 6. MODIFY BOOKING (PUT /api/bookings/{bookingId})
### Updates an existing booking (status, amount, etc.)
PUT {{TravelEase_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerID": 101,
  "partnerID": 5,
  "itemType": "Flight",
  "date": "2026-05-25T14:00:00Z",
  "status": "Confirmed",
  "amount": 349.99
}

###

### 7. CANCEL BOOKING (DELETE /api/bookings/{bookingId})
### Cancels booking and all associated reservations
DELETE {{TravelEase_HostAddress}}/api/bookings/1
Accept: application/json

###

